            <description><![CDATA[【求求了！别再“把背挺直”了！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%235%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%83%E5%87%BA%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%9B%B2%E5%BA%A6%23&amp;extparam=%235%E4%B8%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BB%83%E5%87%BA%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E6%9B%B2%E5%BA%A6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#5个动作练出脊柱健康曲度#</span></a>】其实，后背太直并不是最好的姿势，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%90%8E%E8%83%8C%E5%A4%AA%E7%9B%B4%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%90%8E%E8%83%8C%E5%A4%AA%E7%9B%B4%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E7%A7%8D%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#后背太直可能是种病#</span></a>，平背综合征患者通常腰背部肌肉异常紧张，容易疲劳，站着坐着保持一种姿势就觉得腰酸背痛。5个动作教你保持后背曲度，每个动作做10~15次/组，3组/次，3次/周，快收好👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（人民日报）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvfuduqj20q70q541m.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvg90gmj20pe0mgacu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvfs886j20pm0o4acc.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvfuh5bj20q50oiwht.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvfthv2j20oh0o9776.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhgzvfuy8tj20qd17sjyu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
